從替補席橫空出世
Guy off the end of the bench.

1832
01:22:59,770 --> 01:23:02,170
為所有沒有得到機會的人代言
Speaks for everyone who didn't get their chance.

1833
01:23:02,170 --> 01:23:05,610
只是短短的幾周，在紐約城
It's only a couple of weeks, but in new york city,

1834
01:23:05,610 --> 01:23:07,780
在籃球這一大舞台上
And on basketball's big stage,

1835
01:23:07,780 --> 01:23:09,410
他已經把故事帶出了籃球這個公園
This guy has hit it out of the park.

1836
01:23:11,250 --> 01:23:13,080
在我身上發生的故事
What happened to me, the story that happened to me,

1837
01:23:13,080 --> 01:23:15,250
並不是說，我早就知道
I mean, it wasn't like I knew

1838
01:23:15,250 --> 01:23:17,220
我能從替補席上來完成那些事情
I could just come off the bench and do that.

1839
01:23:17,220 --> 01:23:18,390
我真的不知道
I really didn't.

1840
01:23:18,390 --> 01:23:20,890
我覺得自己有這個水平
Um, I thought I could play at this level,

1841
01:23:20,890 --> 01:23:22,260
我覺得自己可以成為好的球員
And I thought I could be a good player,

1842
01:23:22,260 --> 01:23:24,160
但我沒想到會發生這一系列事情
But I didn't feel like that would happen.

1843
01:23:24,160 --> 01:23:26,960
有些球場上的經歷
And some of those experiences out there when I was on the court,

1844
01:23:26,960 --> 01:23:28,960


1845
01:23:28,970 --> 01:23:31,130
我覺得自己是被別的力量控制著
I felt like I was being controlled by something else.

1846
01:23:31,140 --> 01:23:33,770
有些完全超出肉體
I felt like I was having an out-of-body experience.

1847
01:23:33,770 --> 01:23:35,870
我完成的一些得分
Some of the plays that I made,

1848
01:23:35,870 --> 01:23:37,640
我們的一些勝利
Some of the wins that we had,

1849
01:23:37,640 --> 01:23:40,110
真的超出了這個世界
Were just so out of this world

1850
01:23:40,110 --> 01:23:42,950
我時常還要掐一下自己
That I still have to pinch myself

1851
01:23:42,950 --> 01:23:46,350
才能相信這是真的
To really believe it.

1852
