01:24:36,530 --> 01:24:40,400
{\i1}隨著林書豪翻開新的篇章{\i}
{\i1}As jeremy ends one chapter and begins another,{\i}

1859
01:24:40,400 --> 01:24:44,010
{\i1}前面的路將不斷地考驗他的毅力{\i}
{\i1}The road ahead will continue to test his perseverance.{\i}

1860
01:24:45,180 --> 01:24:48,380
{\i1}他的信念將永遠指引他{\i}
{\i1}But his faith will forever guide him.{\i}

1861
01:24:52,950 --> 01:24:55,150
去年我學會了
The thing I had to learn last year

1862
01:24:55,150 --> 01:24:56,520
完美的計劃並不是
Is a perfect plan doesn't mean

1863
01:24:56,520 --> 01:25:00,490
所有的事情都如你所願
That it ends up the way you want it to end up.

1864
01:25:00,490 --> 01:25:02,760
如果你之前問我，什麼是完美的計劃
In the past, if you asked me what's a perfect plan,

1865
01:25:02,760 --> 01:25:03,960
我可能會答，「心想事成」
I'd be like, "I get what I want,

1866
01:25:03,960 --> 01:25:06,100
「打好球，實現夢想」
I get my dream, I play well."

1867
01:25:09,030 --> 01:25:10,900
現在我有新的看法
Now I have a different perspective

1868
01:25:10,900 --> 01:25:13,440
關於什麼才是完美的計劃
On what a perfect plan is.

1869
01:25:14,840 --> 01:25:17,140
如果你一直贏，你不會成長
You don't get better if you win all the time.

1870
01:25:17,140 --> 01:25:18,940
只有失敗才會讓你成長
You know, you get better when you lose.

1871
01:25:18,940 --> 01:25:20,310
失敗讓你提高
You improve when you lose.

1872
01:25:20,310 --> 01:25:22,210
失敗讓你更加反思自我
You look at yourself more when you lose.

1873
01:25:22,210 --> 01:25:24,850
如果你我都學到很多
So if you learn a lot or if I learn a lot,

1874
01:25:24,850 --> 01:25:26,320
如果我有很好的成長
If I grow a lot,

1875
01:25:26,320 --> 01:25:29,650
如果我隨著時間流逝變成更好的人
If I become a better person through tough times,

1876
01:25:29,650 --> 01:25:31,090
這才是神的完美計劃的一部分
That's part of his perfect plan.

1877
01:25:31,090 --> 01:25:33,060
才是神的完美旨意的一部分
That's part of his perfect will.

1878
01:25:49,840 --> 01:25:52,040
如果我感到缺乏安全感
When I was going through all my insecurities

1879
01:25:52,040 --> 01:25:54,110
失去信心
And uncertainty and lack of confidence,

1880
01:25:54,110 --> 01:25:56,850
那是因為我分散了對神的專注
I was losing focus on god.

1881
01:25:56,850 --> 01:25:58,410
我把注意力放到別的事情上了
I was focusing on all these other things,

1882
01:25:58,420 --> 01:26:02,080
比如我的工作和別人的想法
Like my job and what other people thought of me

1883
01:26:02,090 --> 01:26:05,120
以及各種對我的報道
And what the reporters were writing.

1884
01:26:05,120 --> 01:26:08,820
但隨著時間流逝，我會反思自己
You know, over time, I was able to check myself

1885
01:26:08,830 --> 01:26:10,860
找回我對神的專注
And kind of get my focus back.

1886
01:26:12,260 --> 01:26:14,230
我覺得神對我做了一些超自然的事情
And I think god did something supernatural in me,

1887
01:26:14,230 --> 01:26:17,070
一些我無法以一己之力完成的事情
Something that I couldn't do on my own,

1888
01:26:17,070 --> 01:26:21,000
有些我也許永遠無法複製
Something that I may never be able to recreate.

1889
01:26:22,270 --> 01:26:23,910
所以在那件事上
So I think, in that instance,

1890
01:26:23,910 --> 01:26:27,480
我只是學著去奮鬥
I was just learning to fight

1891
01:26:27,480 --> 01:26:30,510
去為了神而生活和打球
To constantly live and play for god.

1892
01:26:30,510 --> 01:26:34,150
如果我做到這些，我就能完成看似不可能的事情
And when I do that, I'll be able to walk on water.

1893
